ource src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2959560/extras/fd532702e21879349c17c6e0dcfcff1c.webm?t=1730820516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2959560/extras/fd532702e21879349c17c6e0dcfcff1c.mp4?t=1730820516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to take the plunge into the Echoes? Equip yourself, loot, sell, survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Serve the Governor’s vision, ensure your survival, and help reshape this broken world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2959560/extras/105e9a5674bf4b0e69bf0af504cf6b63.poster.avif?t=1730820516\" width=302 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2959560/extras/105e9a5674bf4b0e69bf0af504cf6b63.webm?t=1730820516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2959560/extras/105e9a5674bf4b0e69bf0af504cf6b63.mp4?t=1730820516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
